	Job Opportunities


Every day, we help people around the world make more of their lives through learning. Just like learning, our opportunities take many different forms in lots of areas of expertise.



That’s why we need people as diverse as teachers, journalists, editors, designers, authors, technologists and software engineers to dream up, create, and deliver our products and services for learners everywhere.
Whatever your background, there's a place for you here if you want to make a difference in global education.














	Explore jobs by talent area






Technology

Sales

Research and analytics

Content development






Customer service
Legal
Testing Center
Publishing and editorial






Explore all job opportunities
















We offer competitive benefits
We expect a lot from you, so we give a lot back, with some of the best benefits in the industry.

Learn more










We value diversity and inclusion
We harness the unique skills of each employee and strive to reflect the customers and learners we serve.

Learn more






















